reviewText: I was very pleased with my order.  My order exceeded my expectations.  This DVD has pretty scenery and is a good worship experience.
Love the worship songs on dvd.  Good price.

Great music DVD with high quality audio and graphic backgrounds. My only complaint is that you can't selectively create a playlist, but there is a menu to select individual songs or to play all in sequence.
A great way to start your day out! I pop it into the dvd player and saturate my living area!

These are the best worship videos! The songs are well chosen the editing well done and the creativity is amazing. Every Christian should have some of these for personal worship! Thanks Integrity! You made my time living in Europe not so lonely!
I have used this set many times over. when our praise and worship leader could not be present for services.  It works great!
I would recommend these to anyone who enjoys working in a small group...we enjoy them!
